&lt;h1 id="use-good-notation"&gt;Use good notation&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;By relieving the brain of all unnecessary work, a good notation sets it free to concentrate on more advanced problems, and, in effect, increases the mental power of the race.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;— Alfred North Whitehead, &amp;ldquo;An Introduction to Mathematics&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good notation can make the difference between a readable paper and an unreadable one.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>